# Timestamps
* ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ssZ (e.g., 2026-02-02T14:30:00Z)

# Example HTTP Post Request
```
POST /sensor HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:9100
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 22

{"v":99,"t":34,"h":56}
```
